com.mvohm.quadruple.test

Class IeeeConversionTesterClasses

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mvohm.quadruple.test.IeeeConversionTesterClasses

  • public class IeeeConversionTesterClasses
extends Object
    Contains concrete descendants of the abstract tester classes defined in TesterClasses intended to test conversions from Quadruple to standard IEEE-754 quadruple-precision numbers and vice versa. The general logic of these classes is described in more detail in the descriptions of their respective ancestors such as TesterClasses.Conversion_Q2T_Tester, TesterClasses.Conversion_T2Q_Tester and others, nested in TesterClasses.
    Author:
    M.Vokhmentev
